    "summary": "Deepgram exposes a required-auth HTTP API at api.deepgram.com (use `Authorization: Token <API_KEY>`, with project-scoped API keys from the Console/API and optional short-lived JWTs via token auth), a `dg` CLI (authenticate with `dg login`, `DEEPGRAM_API_KEY`, or `dg --api-key`), and a built-in MCP server at `https://developers.deepgram.com/_mcp/server` that uses the same stored API key, plus a public docs MCP at `https://api.dx.deepgram.com/kapa/mcp` and `https://deepgram.mcp.kapa.ai` that needs no credential.",
