        "generateUrl": "https://console.deepgram.com/signup",
        "setup": "Sign in to the [Deepgram Console](https://console.deepgram.com/signup) and create or copy an API key from your account/project settings. Deepgram’s docs say API keys are used for API access and can be managed in the console or via the API. For the CLI, the easiest path is `dg login`; for scripts/CI you can also pass `--api-key` or set `DEEPGRAM_API_KEY`.",
